INSERT INTO `scene_tbl` VALUES (1,'[NAME]','[NAME]',1,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_0.png',6,'[NAME]'),(2,'Once in a small town, there lived a girl named [NAME]. She loved animals dearly. One sunny morning, while walking to school, [NAME] saw a small, scared puppy hiding under a bush.','Colorful kindergarten building#Flag on the roof#Blue sky with clouds#Red tiled roof#Yellow school bus#Striped awning#Playground slide#Vibrant flowerbeds#Stone pathway#Picket fence#Roundabout road',2,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_1.png',6,'ذات مرة، عاشت فتاة تدعى [NAME] في بلدة صغيرة. كانت تحب الحيوانات كثيرا. في صباح أحد الأيام المشمسة، أثناء سيره إلى المدرسة، رأى [NAME] جروًا صغيرًا خائفًا يختبئ تحت الأدغال.'),(3,'[NAME] gently approached the puppy. Don\'t be scared, she whispered. The puppy, wagging its tail, peeked out. You\'re lost, aren\'t you? [NAME] thought. She knew she had to help.','Schoolyard with playground#Children playing#Sports courts (basketball and soccer)#School building#Blue sky with fluffy clouds#Green trees#Lush grass#Urban background with skyscrapers#School flag#Park benches#Toy balls',3,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_2.png',6,'[الاسم] اقترب بلطف من الجرو. همست: لا تخافوا. وألقى الجرو نظرة خاطفة على الخارج وهو يهز ذيله. أنت ضائع، أليس كذلك؟ فكر [الاسم]. كانت تعلم أن عليها المساعدة.'),(4,'At school, [NAME] told her friends about the puppy. Let\'s start a pet rescue mission! exclaimed her friend, Mia. They all agreed. It was time to help the lost and stray pets!','Outdoor school playground#Green trees and bushes#School building with clock#Basketball court#Swings and slides#Bench and picnic table#Fenced grass area#Colorful balls#Paved pathway',4,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_3.png',6,'في المدرسة، أخبرت [NAME] أصدقاءها عن الجرو. لنبدأ مهمة إنقاذ الحيوانات الأليفة! صاحت صديقتها، ميا. اتفقوا جميعا. لقد حان الوقت لمساعدة الحيوانات الأليفة الضالة والضالة!'),(5,'They made colorful posters and put them around the neighborhood. Help us find homes for lost pets! the posters read. The children felt excited to make a difference.\n','Classroom interior#Blackboard with math equations#Student character#Educational toys and blocks#Wall clock#Storage shelves with books and materials#Potted plants#Cloud and arithmetic symbols',5,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_4.png',6,'لقد صنعوا ملصقات ملونة ووزعوها في جميع أنحاء الحي. ساعدونا في العثور على منازل للحيوانات الأليفة المفقودة! قراءة الملصقات. شعر الأطفال بالحماس لإحداث فرق.'),(6,'Soon, people started calling. We found a kitten! or There\'s a lost bunny here! The children were busy. Every pet mattered to them.\n','Fruit-themed math garden#Numbered fruit trees (apple, orange)#Addition and subtraction signs#Fruit baskets#Wooden fence with math problems#Stone pathway#Lush vegetation and flowers ',6,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_5.png',6,'وسرعان ما بدأ الناس في الاتصال. وجدنا قطة صغيرة! أو هناك أرنب ضائع هنا! كان الأطفال مشغولين. كل حيوان أليف مهم بالنسبة لهم.'),(7,'They took care of each animal. They fed them, cleaned them, and gave them love. [NAME] felt happy seeing the animals getting healthier and happier.\n','Orchard with arithmetic operations#Flying apples with numbers#Sun and clouds#Orange and apple trees#Flowerbeds#Wooden footbridge#River',7,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_6.png',6,'لقد اعتنوا بكل حيوان. لقد أطعموهم ونظفوهم وأعطوهم الحب. شعر [NAME] بالسعادة عندما رأى الحيوانات تصبح أكثر صحة وسعادة.'),(8,'The children found families who wanted pets. We promise to love and care for them, the families would say. Each goodbye was bittersweet but happy.\n','Classroom setting#Chalkboard with numbers#Desks with books and notebooks#World globes#Bookshelves with colorful bins#Hanging ceiling lights#Clock and wall decorations',8,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_7.png',6,'وجد الأطفال عائلات تريد حيوانات أليفة. تقول العائلات: نحن نعد بأن نحبهم ونعتني بهم. كان كل وداع حلو ومر ولكنه سعيد.'),(9,'One day, the mayor visited. You kids are our town\'s heroes! he said. He gave them a special award for their kindness and hard work.\n','Bright classroom with colorful decor#Blackboard with educational drawings#Rainbow carpet#Desks with school supplies#Shelves filled with books#Educational posters#World map',9,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_8.png',6,'في أحد الأيام، زار العمدة. أنتم أيها الأطفال أبطال مدينتنا! هو قال. وقدم لهم جائزة خاصة على لطفهم وعملهم الجاد.'),(10,'[NAME]','[NAME]',1,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_0.png',4,'[NAME]'),(11,'[NAME] stood brave amidst chaos. His city burned, but hope sparked within him. Donning his cape, he was ready to rise from the ashes, a young hero facing a fiery trial.','Hovering Hero#Serene Confidence#Skyline Backdrop#Focused Gaze#Iconic Suit#Red and Blue#City Protector#Superhuman Flight#Teenage Resilience#Heightened Perspective#Calm Amidst Chaos#Vigilant Guardian#Symbol of Hope#Wind-Swept Hair#Optimistic Future',2,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_1.png',4,'[NAME] وقف شجاعًا وسط الفوضى. احترقت مدينته، لكن الأمل انبثق بداخله. كان يرتدي عباءته، وكان مستعدًا للنهوض من الرماد، كبطل شاب يواجه محاكمة نارية.'),(12,'[NAME] soared above the city, his cape fluttering in the wind. The people below looked up, marveling at the young hero who watched over them. With a heart full of courage, [NAME] was ready to protect his home.','Ascending Hero#Determined Eyes#Skyward Focus#Youthful Bravery#Superhero Flight#Ember Sparks#Urban Savior#Resolute Expression#Iconic Emblem#Vivid Imagery#Action Pose#Defender of Justice#Rising Above#Cityscape Below#Dynamic Movement',3,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_2.png',4,'طفل خارق يلعب في حديقة مشمسة. يمكن رؤية المباني الشاهقة من بعيد. هناك معدات لعب ممتعة وعشب أخضر وسحب مبتسمة.'),(13,'In the heart of the city, [NAME] flew in his red and blue suit, piercing the sky with defiance. The wind caressed his brave face, and his eyes vigilantly surveyed the city from above. Soaring like an eagle, he was ready to bestow safety upon anyone who called for him.','Epic Hero#Explosion#Firestorm#Debris#Unscathed#Mighty Stance#Cape Billowing#Destruction#Fearless#Savior#Powerful Silhouette#Skyscrapers#Calm Amidst Chaos#Defender#Invincible',4,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_3.png',4,'عربي'),(14,'Amidst the roaring flames and falling debris, [NAME] stood resilient. His suit, a beacon of strength, shone against the fire\'s rage. This was his trial by fire, and he would emerge a hero.','Wounded Warrior#Battle Aftermath#Dusty Ruins#Pensive Stare#Tattered Symbol#Young Resilience#Sunbeam Illumination#Abandoned Building#Subdued Colors#Survivor#Quiet Determination#Shadow and Light#Standoff#Hope Amidst Despair#Torn Cape',5,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_4.png',4,'عربي'),(15,'In a desolate building scarred by battle, [NAME]\'s eyes held a silent story. His torn suit whispered of his undying spirit, standing amidst ruins, the young guardian remained an unwavering symbol of resilience.','Revealing Identity#Damaged Hero#Dark Shadows#Intense Gaze#Frayed Rope#Youthful Determination#Costume Torn#Inner Strength#Secret Power#Stark Contrast#Grim Setting#Resolute Youngster#Hidden Depths#Symbolic Gesture#Toughened Survivor',6,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_5.png',4,'عربي'),(16,'[NAME], with a gaze as steely as his resolve, revealed the emblem beneath his torn cape. In the dim light, his eyes shone with unspoken stories of bravery. Today, he was not just a boy; he was the symbol of hope in a weary world.','Heroic Stride#Caped Crusader#Wet Ground#Determined March#Reflective Surface#Modern Architecture#Evening Patrol#Muscular Silhouette#Focused Vigilance#Red Cape Flowing#Blue Suit#Iconic Emblem#Strong Jawline#Underground Parking#Dynamic Movement',7,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_6.png',4,'عربي'),(17,'Under the shimmering lights of the city\'s heartbeat, [NAME] raced forward. The echoes of his cape in the wind, a rhythmic beat against the silence of the night. He was a shadow, a guardian, a silent promise to the sleeping world.','Bruised Adolescent#Defiant Stance#Police Escort#Corridor Standoff#Blue Suit#Red Cape#Injured Hero#Pensive Expression#Wet Hair#Subdued Lighting#Scratched Emblem#Youthful Courage#Authority Presence#Protective Gear#Quiet Resolve',8,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_7.png',4,'عربي'),(26,'Today is a sunny Friday. [NAME] is excited. He decides to visit the forest nearby. He imagines tall trees and animals. He puts on his shoes, takes a small bag, and starts walking. He can\'t wait to see what he\'ll find. The forest looks green and big. He steps in, ready for adventure.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',2,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_1.png',7,'اليوم يوم جمعة مشمس. [NAME] متحمس. يقرر زيارة الغابة القريبة. يتخيل الأشجار الطويلة والحيوانات. يرتدي حذائه ويأخذ حقيبة صغيرة ويبدأ بالمشي. لا يمكنه الانتظار ليرى ما سيجده. تبدو الغابة خضراء وكبيرة. يتدخل وهو جاهز للمغامرة.'),(27,'First, he sees deer. They are eating grass in a clearing. Their eyes are gentle. [NAME] watches quietly. The deer seem calm and free. He feels happy just looking at them. They don\'t notice him. He takes out his notebook and writes, \"Deer are peaceful.\" He smiles and walks on.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',3,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_2.png',7,'أولا يرى الغزلان. إنهم يأكلون العشب في المقاصة. عيونهم لطيفة. [NAME] يشاهد بهدوء. يبدو الغزلان هادئًا وحرًا. إنه يشعر بالسعادة بمجرد النظر إليهم. لا يلاحظونه. أخرج دفتر ملاحظاته وكتب: \"الغزلان مسالمة\". يبتسم ويمضي.'),(28,'[NAME] finds a place with many butterflies. They fly around him. Their wings have many colors like a rainbow. They land softly on flowers. Some fly close to him. He tries to count them but there are too many. It\'s like a dream. He feels like he\'s in a fairy tale.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',4,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_3.png',7,'[NAME] يجد مكانًا به العديد من الفراشات. يطيرون حوله. أجنحتها لها ألوان كثيرة مثل قوس قزح. يهبطون بهدوء على الزهور. والبعض يطير بالقرب منه. يحاول عدهم ولكن هناك الكثير منهم. انها مثل حلم. يشعر وكأنه في قصة خيالية.'),(29,'Next, he hears laughter. It\'s monkeys! They swing from tree to tree. They play tag and chase each other. They seem to be having fun. [NAME] laughs too. The monkeys are funny and full of energy. He wishes he could climb trees like them. He watches them for a long time.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',5,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_4.png',7,'وبعد ذلك يسمع الضحك. إنها القرود! يتأرجحون من شجرة إلى أخرى. يلعبون العلامة ويطاردون بعضهم البعض. يبدو أنهم يستمتعون. [NAME] يضحك أيضًا. القرود مضحكة ومليئة بالطاقة. يتمنى أن يتمكن من تسلق الأشجار مثلهم. يراقبهم لفترة طويلة.'),(30,'Then, [NAME] spots a fox. It walks with soft steps. He reads in his book, \"Foxes are clever.\" The fox has a red coat and sharp ears. It looks around and then disappears into the bushes. [NAME] feels excited to see a fox. He never saw one before today.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',6,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_5.png',7,'ثم اكتشف [NAME] ثعلبًا. يمشي بخطوات ناعمة. يقرأ في كتابه \"الثعالب ذكية\". الثعلب لديه معطف أحمر وآذان حادة. ينظر حوله ثم يختفي في الأدغال. [NAME] يشعر بالإثارة لرؤية ثعلب. ولم ير واحدة قبل اليوم.'),(31,'It\'s time for lunch. [NAME] sits under a big tree. He eats his sandwiches. He shares a piece with a squirrel. The squirrel takes it and runs up the tree. [NAME] laughs. He watches the squirrels play. They jump from branch to branch. Lunchtime with squirrels is fun.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',7,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_6.png',7,'إنه وقت الغداء. [NAME] يجلس تحت شجرة كبيرة. يأكل شطائره. يتقاسم قطعة مع السنجاب. يأخذها السنجاب ويركض نحو الشجرة. [الاسم] يضحك. يشاهد السناجب تلعب. يقفزون من فرع إلى فرع. وقت الغداء مع السناجب ممتع.'),(32,'[NAME] walks to a small creek. He sees frogs jumping. Snakes are swimming in the water. They move without a sound. He sits and watches. The frogs say, \"Ribbit.\" The water is clear. He can see small fish too. The creek is full of life. It\'s a new world for him.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',8,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_7.png',7,'[NAME] يسير إلى جدول صغير. يرى الضفادع تقفز. الثعابين تسبح في الماء. يتحركون بدون صوت. يجلس ويشاهد. الضفادع تقول \"ريبت\". الماء واضح. يمكنه رؤية الأسماك الصغيرة أيضًا. الخور مليء بالحياة. إنه عالم جديد بالنسبة له.'),(33,'He finds a place with many birds. They are singing. There are big birds and small birds. Birds with long tails and birds with bright feathers. They sing different songs. It\'s like music. [NAME] closes his eyes and listens. The bird songs make him feel calm and happy.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',9,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_8.png',7,'يجد مكانًا به العديد من الطيور. انهم يغنون. هناك الطيور الكبيرة والطيور الصغيرة. الطيور ذات الذيول الطويلة والطيور ذات الريش اللامع. يغنون أغاني مختلفة. إنها مثل الموسيقى. [NAME] يغلق عينيه ويستمع. أغاني الطيور تجعله يشعر بالهدوء والسعادة.'),(34,'[NAME] sits on a rock. He thinks about the forest. He understands it\'s a special place. We must take care of it. He feels lucky to be there. The trees, the animals, they all have a home here. He wants to help keep the forest safe for them.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',10,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_9.png',7,'[NAME] يجلس على صخرة. يفكر في الغابة. إنه يفهم أنه مكان خاص. يجب أن نعتني به. إنه يشعر بأنه محظوظ لوجوده هناك. الأشجار، الحيوانات، جميعهم لديهم منزل هنا. يريد المساعدة في الحفاظ على الغابة آمنة لهم.'),(35,'Book Title','Book Title',1,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_0.png',7,'عربي'),(36,'High above the city, [NAME] flew with fierce determination. His eyes, reflecting the inferno below, were resolute. This young hero was not just soaring; he was ascending as a beacon of hope, his spirit unbroken by the flames.','Hopeful Youth#Superhero Costume#City Crowd#Sunset Glow#Upward Gaze#Inspirational Moment#Curious Expression#Golden Hour#Aspiring Hero#Casual Stance#Public Admiration#Urban Backdrop#Iconic Cape#Dreamful Eyes#Everyday Champion',10,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_9.png',4,'عربي'),(37,'[NAME] stood amidst the city bustle, his youthful eyes filled with wonder. The setting sun cast a golden glow on his face, a stark contrast to the iconic suit that hinted at the extraordinary within an ordinary world.','Soaring Escape#Red Cape#Industrial Setting#Mystic Flight#Nighttime Adventure#Dramatic Lighting#Neon Ambiance#Urban Hero#Action Shot#Speed#Freedom#Powerful Leap#Mysterious Vigilante#Energetic Rush#Dynamic Pose',11,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_A.png',4,'عربي'),(38,'[NAME] leaned against the cold wall, the battle\'s scars visible on his face. Behind him, the police stood ready. He might be bruised, but his eyes held the unyielding spirit of a hero, prepared for whatever challenge came next.','Aerial Vigilance#Youthful Superhero#Determined Gaze#Soaring Above#City Inferno#Curling Smoke#Red Cape Billowing#Iconic Emblem#Fiery Sky#Hero\'s Resolve#Sharp Contours#Rooftop Perspective#Urban Guardian#Emerging Leader#Dawn of Hope',9,'/assets/bundles/superman/Swap_8.png',4,'عربي'),(39,'Walking back home, [NAME] feels happy. He remembers the deer, the monkeys, the fox, and the birds. He can\'t wait to tell his family about his day. He knows he will come back to the forest again. It\'s a place full of wonders and adventures.','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',11,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_A.png',7,'عند العودة إلى المنزل، يشعر [NAME] بالسعادة. يتذكر الغزلان والقرود والثعلب والطيور. لا يستطيع الانتظار ليخبر عائلته عن يومه. إنه يعلم أنه سيعود إلى الغابة مرة أخرى. إنه مكان مليء بالعجائب والمغامرات.'),(40,'BackPage','Vibrant alien landscape#Friendly monster aliens#Planets and moons#Spacecraft and flying objects#Intergalactic playground',12,'/assets/bundles/zoo/Swap_B.png',7,'عربي'),(41,'Looking at all the happy pets with their new families, [NAME] felt proud. We did this together, she smiled. The Pet Rescue Mission was a success!\n','Bright classroom with colorful decor#Blackboard with educational drawings#Rainbow carpet#Desks with school supplies#Shelves filled with books#Educational posters#World map',10,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_9.png',6,'عربي'),(42,'From that day, [NAME] and her friends continued to help animals. Everyone knew them as the kind kids who loved pets. And the pets loved them back, forever.\n','Bright classroom with colorful decor#Blackboard with educational drawings#Rainbow carpet#Desks with school supplies#Shelves filled with books#Educational posters#World map',11,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_A.png',6,'عربي'),(43,'backpage','Bright classroom with colorful decor#Blackboard with educational drawings#Rainbow carpet#Desks with school supplies#Shelves filled with books#Educational posters#World map',12,'/assets/bundles/school/Swap_B.png',6,'عربي');
